Server setup I've run for a few Drupal 8 sites I'm running. New to doing this, the following is some what I've learned in the last few months.

--Update and upgrade Ubuntu--
sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get upgrade -y
sudo apt-get dist-upgrade -y
sudo apt-get autoremove -y

--Apache install--
sudo apt-get install apache2 -y
sudo apt-get install apache2-utils -y
sudo service apache2 restart

--PHP package upgrade--
sudo apt-get install -y language-pack-en-base
sudo LC_ALL=en_US.UTF-8 add-apt-repository ppa:ondrej/php5-5.6
sudo add-apt-repository ppa:ondrej/php5-5.6
sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install python-software-properties
sudo apt-get update

--PHP install and mod enable--
sudo apt-get install php5 php5-cli php5-fpm php5-gd libssh2-php libapache2-mod-php5 php5-mcrypt php5-mysql php5-curl php5-json -y  
sudo a2enmod rewrite headers
sudo service apache2 restart
sudo php5enmod mcrypt

--MySQL install--
sudo apt-get install mysql-server-5.6
sudo mysql_secure_installation
sudo service mysql restart
